Meet the Black Woman Revolutionizing Eyewear Care! 🙌🏾⁠
⁠
Dori Young, the inventor and founder of Clean Peepers (@eyeglasseggs), has created the world’s first game-changing eyewear cleaning product—and it’s a must-have! Inspired by her family’s legacy of innovation and her own struggles keeping glasses spotless, she turned a brilliant idea into reality.⁠
⁠
From concept to company, marketing, and motherhood, Dori’s journey is nothing short of inspiring.⁠
⁠
Tap the link in our bio or head to blog.obws.com to read her full story!⁠
